{"title":"Subluxación Atlantoaxoidea como complicación de enfermedades reumatológicas-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Reumatología/Subluxación Atlantoaxoidea como complicación de enfermedades reumatológicas-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Subluxación Atlantoaxoidea como\\Ncomplicación de enfermedades reumatológicas","guid":"e2G_IzLZseAGldGsWQx8Bw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Caso clínico:","guid":"dBf2QTthEHg9EfuQTcbKTg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Información del Paciente:","guid":"LjR-bCf-MuAXwpfia4w1fg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"- Edad: 58 años","guid":"TlI7KinaJNEw8g1qGgJwkQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"- Sexo: Femenino","guid":"IRNJ11oNePIpykjfTfk83w","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"- Antecedentes médicos: Diagnosticada con artritis reumatoide desde hace 10 años,\\Nen tratamiento con metotrexato y prednisona. Con mala adherencia a tratamiento.","guid":"Dk1yYCtiNsICDQbRf-0btg","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- Motivo de Consulta:","guid":"TKGkLBTlRL0WnOfeQLmabg","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- \"Dolor severo en la nuca y rigidez, que ha empeorado en los últimos meses.\"","guid":"UEZVNlOu424OgGS8ZoMQFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"- Examen Físico:","guid":"PhIwAHfXD7x21pSAU8sNBQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"- Inspección: Cabeza inclinada hacia adelante, incapaz de levantarla completamente.","guid":"fBRWHVmcPhw_Ao7XKkjUiQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"- Palpación: Sensibilidad sobre la región cervical alta.","guid":"AZpw_FbFJrkV1QoHT-ysJg","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"- Movilidad: Movimiento cervical severamente restringido y doloroso.","guid":"AJ9LikbHF3Fp7xy3IbKVYQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"- Neurológico: Déficit de fuerza en extremidades superiores, hipoestesia en dermatomas C4-C6.","guid":"INSQZBO5ZZZvq9JALyICxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"- Laboratorio:","guid":"PxucWHG42REvDx57C71AhQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"- Marcadores inflamatorios: VSG 68 mm/h, PCR 25 mg/L (elevados).","guid":"Bp4dz0WsBllMdtrzVuRzBQ","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"- Factor reumatoide y anti-CCP positivos","guid":"GVrpx1r3P689Z4MaV20Zxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"- Diagnóstico:","guid":"Us5PazQ-F5orOCbMTuKliQ","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- RM cervical: Subluxación de C1 sobre C2 con señales de\\Nerosión del ligamento transverso y compresión medular leve.","guid":"DdpVt2o6taN5K3oSD3TGsw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"- Radiografías cervicales: Confirmación de la subluxación atlantoaxoidea.","guid":"QP_cXA8AhBpfYXLaQZ8n5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"- Manejo:","guid":"Vcebi0lQj5FjUb1Hdpwr7w","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"- Médico: Incremento en la dosificación de prednisona, inicio de terapia\\Nbiológica con infliximab para controlar la actividad de la AR.","guid":"XQn1KFL9j4glvi60HCWRgA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"- Quirúrgico: Evaluación para fusión cervical anterior C1-C2 para estabilización.","guid":"RLZomVTNTS8n4tIFS1SGaA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"- Soporte: Uso de collarín cervical rígido para minimizar\\Nel movimiento y prevenir daños adicionales.","guid":"GnlTiHRZrPgiOPltM9Q9Tw","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"1","text":"- Seguimiento:","guid":"T1Dsp1-gfIgLQVcWIh88Ew","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"- Reevaluación clínica y por RM a las 4 semanas para\\Nevaluar la respuesta al tratamiento y planificar la cirugía.","guid":"E96UIjZ5feJxAeGcIbjp2Q","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"- Visitas de seguimiento cada 3 meses para ajustar\\Nla terapia y monitorear la función neurológica.","guid":"ILQzhWotW64xLbCNYbQP4Q","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"- Rehabilitación física postquirúrgica para\\Nmejorar la movilidad y fuerza muscular.","guid":"eS3fyBCPI2cjUzfHTvV7VA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"cZ-pViE_bWoS2D3sFq_MJw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"- ¿Cuál es la principal enfermedad reumatológica asociada a subluxación atlantoaxoidea? Artritis Reumatoide (AR) (1).","guid":"BhdqX0Z3BrdgKTnAakgzQQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"- ¿Cuál es el riesgo de mielopatía cervical en pacientes con AR? Hasta un 58% (2).","guid":"Jy6UMX0UW-ks8-i3Kt3xbg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"- ¿Cuál es el \"Gold Standard\" diagnóstico? RM de columna cervical (3).","guid":"Skgvm2r3Ro5ZQOX6Bute8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"- Subluxación de la articulación entre el atlas (C1) y el axis (C2), principalmente por inestabilidad ligamentosa (4).","guid":"YhiyKmozhSgHRwGReIG-Ww","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"- Inflamación crónica sinovial y ligamentosa → Laxitud ligamentosa → Inestabilidad atlantoaxoidea (6).","guid":"JHXnaUk2qkIxCC89H9emjA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"- Erosiones óseas y quistes subcondrales contribuyen a la inestabilidad (7).","guid":"fBBcIzeeAOl45CKUVYTZmA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"- Potencial compresión medular por subluxación (8).","guid":"Jqj-viUNpVEnYvNyLMBpHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"- AR es la principal enfermedad reumatológica asociada, con prevalencia de 0,46% en Chile (9).","guid":"a4SsCAeMLTIXCJxfErNAOg","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"- Hasta un 80% de los pacientes con AR tienen compromiso cervical, siendo la subluxación atlantoaxoidea la más frecuente (10).","guid":"BKCJG0P8hRc9kTGoTui4tg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"- Mayor prevalencia en AR de larga data (11).","guid":"LvPLpRbSF6JV1BemEQx9zw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"Causas:","guid":"V8yhIWGKPvk3hDfcgY847w","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- AR (70-80%) (15).","guid":"Uf7zBDo50pxd6AsbeKfxwg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"- Espondilitis Anquilosante (EA) (10-15%) (16).","guid":"X0d37gVK_o0laFrgSswj9g","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"- Artritis Idiopática Juvenil (AIJ) (5-10%) (17).","guid":"DNcrwDxw90Bdf2QwEXe02w","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"- Otros: Síndrome de Down, Síndrome de Marfan, etc. (<5%) (18).","guid":"AG18VxsQldhgYG2SL2FH_A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- AR seropositiva (FR y/o anti-CCP) (RR: 2,5) (12).","guid":"AQWcyl0bGTcJjjwqarxgeg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"- Edad > 65 años (RR: 1,8) (13).","guid":"fQgiEkMcKx1pWMLeIX4JfA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"- Sexo femenino (RR: 1,5) (14).","guid":"DFLVXxpg8htBVbAICGMxgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- Dolor cervical insidioso (80%) (19).","guid":"MeKtejY0hThAbcXLMuhKRA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"- Rigidez cervical matinal (60%) (20).","guid":"E0-ecEn8AfUdpKq-EFfAgg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"- Cefalea occipital (40%) (21).","guid":"DRgtEgb9bZwx1cn-GWsCcg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"- Marcha inestable (20%) (22).","guid":"IV5ft3MregchzjP0c11Suw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"- Signos de compresión medular: Hiperreflexia, Babinski, Hoffman, Lhermitte (10%) (23).","guid":"LWVMo3-2Pw9sBUR-DKzEkQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Radiografía cervical dinámica (Sensibilidad: 70%, Especificidad: 80%) (25).","guid":"Td6WnjT4TLgjUB44TkwS9Q","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- RM de columna cervical (Sensibilidad: 90%, Especificidad: 95%) (26).","guid":"UAjikQOwi8p9rVrxAeuQCw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"- TC de columna cervical (Sensibilidad: 80%, Especificidad: 90%) (27).","guid":"OeURAz4bILw009pQTTSvcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- Clínico + Imágenes (28).","guid":"CBcislJ4hQ5djG_1FS9PxA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Diagnóstico de trabajo: Subluxación atlantoaxoidea (29).","guid":"WXXyqw9iOfQumlI2etRSYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"- \"Gold Standard\" diagnóstico: RM de columna cervical (30).","guid":"Ao2z-1BohituMaUeL_MAng","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"- Criterios diagnósticos: Distancia atlantodental > 3 mm en radiografía o RM (31).","guid":"UB7FOlo26Zw8n8UwVSAC1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos diferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"- Síndrome doloroso cervical mecánico (32).","guid":"a6SI-hQYrbhm-Gw0OYMfmQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"- Discopatía cervical (33).","guid":"SRD6cApIim0HzzKOGRndAQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"- Espondiloartritis (34).","guid":"DfkWNwV8jYAbBW0NR94nOg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"- Mielopatía espondilótica cervical (35).","guid":"Q5euPE_ZR10VEtatS67Q7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Objetivo: Aliviar dolor y prevenir mielopatía cervical (36).","guid":"IlHMa3KfRqNg3iCze8e_Fg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"- No farmacológico: Inmovilización cervical con collar blando (37).","guid":"AgGAlw94cul2nBF5BI80kg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"- Farmacológico:","guid":"X-D5FGTNtpc0gjUwL_--Tw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"* Prednisona 0,5 mg/kg/día con reducción gradual.","guid":"BTqoGGwYLVtkLEjGTkuiiQ","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"* Metotrexato 7,5 mg/sem VO o SC, con aumentos de 2,5 mg/sem hasta 25 mg/sem.","guid":"dmC3yGv7e1VnZX-KBFnN_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"70","text":"- Quirúrgico: Fijación cervical posterior C1-C2, en casos de mielopatía (39).","guid":"cXgI1QJq7JdMN_U6NQ-3EQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y pronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- Evaluación clínica y con imágenes cada 6-12 meses (40).","guid":"UkQz9GFKy-cAvogAdJYAYA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"- Peor pronóstico si hay mielopatía al diagnóstico (41).","guid":"U-oSimGcqLNwXb92VeuTIQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"- Seguimiento por reumatólogo, traumatólogo y fisiatra (42).","guid":"cRUbnGb50O9aesezUPYUsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"- Control estricto de la actividad inflamatoria en AR (43).","guid":"S8eHhg78_OQA9dMACswnuQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"- Detección precoz de compromiso cervical en AR (44).","guid":"AB73RAYVlCY1dVDnBVmfXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"- Radiografía cervical dinámica en pacientes con AR, especialmente con factores de riesgo\\N(Sensibilidad: 70%, Especificidad: 80%) (45).","guid":"ci3BgRmhma1TpUHmaI55SQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"- Mayor riesgo de mielopatía (46).","guid":"BZ0VAjsKwXBs6EdJdxUd1w","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"- Considerar comorbilidades y polifarmacia para tratamiento (47).","guid":"PXWuCDkgPIMsJNTpD7nh_A","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"- Rehabilitación precoz para evitar síndrome de desacondicionamiento (48).","guid":"GmsIaizjXOkET-JcblUa9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"1. Arthritis Rheum. 2006;54(10):3452-64.","guid":"DoAFnHStodNEQK4Wf5UhOA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"2. J Rheumatol. 1994;21(1):177-9.","guid":"W6dywh67dcpQizXpJ276SQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"3. Ann Rheum Dis. 2016;75(10):1789-96.","guid":"LbhyrlGBCOkyOyICLddp8g","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"4. Neuroimaging Clin N Am. 2019;29(4):581-598.","guid":"V5adEGewcukzMQlPScRekQ","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"5. Br Med J. 1890; 1(1516):821.","guid":"AVIMlwbWSzUyUtfbBu8hmQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"6-48. (Referencias\\Nomitidas para abreviar)","guid":"QeEMph87HyR-BD9xf1a6rg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":96,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Reumatología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Reumatología","filename":"Subluxación Atlantoaxoidea como complicación de enfermedades reumatológicas-2024-1","id":"map_2209","resolved_references":[]}